      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm stuck at Heathrow right now. My connecting flight to Singapore just got canceled and everything is a mess here. I need to get there as fast as possible. Can you help me figure out what kind of alternative routes I should be looking for to minimize my total travel time? I'm trying to decide if I should look for a direct flight from a different hub or if a multi-stop route through Doha or Dubai would actually be quicker given the current delays.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
